le":"見出し画像","target":"https://assets.st-note.com/production/uploads/images/177976113/rectangle_large_type_2_6983b0e36710d4325a4671c1cda253de.jpeg?width=1200","line":15},{"title":"honeshabri","target":"https://note.com/honeshabri","line":19},{"title":"画像","target":"https://assets.st-note.com/img/1741356874-paQXOMmgYnrWfxsqFezCKJNd.png","line":25},{"title":"マシュマロ","target":"https://marshmallow-qa.com/messages/ed63cf02-d2ad-4b8c-97c8-55263b59813a","line":27},{"title":"画像","target":"https://assets.st-note.com/img/1741357154-V5WPEqpKUA7HQTFBbxXv9wmO.png?width=1200","line":65},{"title":"日本国内で移住するならどこがいいか","target":"https://note.com/honeshabri/n/na90bd144f88e","line":69},{"title":"画像","target":"https://assets.st-note.com/img/1741357176-DmARExTuKWic2peClnwLvoj6.png?width=1200","line":71},{"title":"ノート名","target":"ノート名","line":90},{"title":"ノート名","target":"ノート名","line":97},{"title":"ノート名1","target":"ノート名1","line":115},{"title":"ノート名2","target":"ノート名2","line":116},{"title":"ノート名3","target":"ノート名3","line":119},{"title":"ノート名4","target":"ノート名4","line":120},{"title":"ノート名5","target":"ノート名5","line":123},{"title":"ノート名6","target":"ノート名6","line":124},{"title":"画像","target":"https://assets.st-note.com/img/1741357563-EuS3xnwAqNDHQ0PjcmoXF6bp.png?width=1200","line":140},{"title":"画像","target":"https://assets.st-note.com/img/1741357314-1l2MDaPAFHXRg8SqOQrWytVL.png?width=1200","line":146},{"title":"**Throw a marshmallow to 骨しゃぶり | Marshmallow** *Accepting anonymous messages. はてブとニチアサ実況するブロガー* *marshmallow-qa.com*","target":"https://marshmallow-qa.com/honeshabri","line":164}],"metadata":{"title":"Obsidianでのメモ整理はリンク中心｜honeshabri","source":"https://note.com/honeshabri/n/nf288b0d28893","author":["[[note（ノート）]]"],"published":"2025-03-07","created":"2025-04-18","description":"マシュマロに答える。 マシュマロ この質問、非常に身につまされる内容だ。メモを取ることとメモを活用することは全く別のスキルであり、多くの人が後者で躓いている。特にデジタルツールを使うと、「取る→忘れる→探せない→あきらめる」という悪循環に陥りがちだ。  ここでは、Obsidianを使ったメモ整理について、一般的なベストプラクティスを簡単に紹介した上で、俺自身が実践している方法を詳しく解説したい。  Obsidianでメモを整理する一般的なアプローチ  Obsidianでメモを管理する一般的な方法としては、以下のようなものがある。    フォルダ・タグ・リンクの組み合わせ：カテゴリごとの","tags":["Later","🎁Topic/","Scrap"],"image":"https://assets.st-note.com/production/uploads/images/177976113/rectangle_large_type_2_6983b0e36710d4325a4671c1cda253de.jpeg?fit=bounds&quality=85&width=1280"},"last_embed":{"hash":"fx1v6o","at":1751263471513}},"smart_blocks:300_Input/Obsidianでのメモ整理はリンク中心｜honeshabri.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06210148,-0.04456791,0.04343402,-0.04233405,-0.02916623,-0.00268582,0.0013787,0.05296939,-0.01278189,0.05940425,-0.02850897,-0.09844059,0.04157905,0.04811055,0.02062481,0.03916378,0.0188608,-0.00412737,-0.02420871,0.00536045,0.1561867,0.00135402,0.0615588,-0.03399944,-0.03315752,0.00968193,0.04625885,-0.01398767,-0.01306758,-0.17784601,-0.05559767,0.021316,0.01121086,-0.02512719,-0.00049121,-0.03780753,-0.03776916,-0.02852745,-0.03555694,0.06436439,-0.0158717,0.03590961,0.01020663,-0.02835363,-0.01442094,-0.0261253,-0.04440869,-0.02177435,0.04644943,-0.00009705,-0.01242035,-0.00422458,0.07957368,0.00338258,0.08070568,-0.01249791,0.06387051,0.06095316,0.05867058,0.04555472,0.05247931,0.01797502,-0.16733347,0.05462491,0.03048771,0.00071047,-0.04575712,-0.01762427,-0.01279424,-0.0112193,0.01342634,0.04755696,0.0163898,0.05112666,0.04272242,-0.00776415,0.03006215,-0.0602131,-0.02606151,0.01108267,0.01296312,0.02427645,-0.00059672,-0.00797609,-0.02955587,-0.02722809,0.04683162,-0.00147794,0.01644053,0.00188602,-0.03305585,-0.02288729,0.00280449,0.00351355,-0.05306194,-0.01972903,0.03705302,0.03800924,-0.03762406,0.09601248,-0.02422579,-0.0064492,-0.0188553,-0.08027821,0.0583996,0.03268098,0.00758175,-0.00399952,-0.01934207,0.03258127,-0.01810424,-0.04394386,0.01970799,-0.04405929,0.01884602,0.05101663,0.0341813,-0.01794093,0.00288535,-0.02938463,-0.00829267,0.00601564,0.0037262,-0.02887652,0.02267644,-0.01585074,0.04347385,0.04408118,0.07833122,0.10123815,0.02415735,-0.01952181,-0.09522913,-0.02365854,-0.03